Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你听到这段话时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.87,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(840,611)\blur2}（夏威夷生存圈）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22世纪 对人类来说已成战争时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:34.59,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,0)\blur2\pos(656,611)}（波莉亚胡运输基地）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自遥远宇宙的未知存在 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们拥有超越人类理解范围的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自40年前它们出现在这颗星球上以来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球大半土地都已化作战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落前60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照作战行动 迅速加入前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是通过了严苛训练
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活至今的精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够与你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深以为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号机 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比报告说的还严重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:15.95,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,663)}Second machine Olympia-Angels,landing check
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号机 奥林匹亚天使 着陆检查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要像哥哥一样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五号机 出动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Festum专用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考控制体感操纵式有人兵器Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被选中的人才能开动 是我们的杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认类型1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意类型4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内置敌人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其力量为人类所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有Fafner 我们或许早就灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使胜利遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们争取到了足以获得希望的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒纳凯阿前哨基地陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有功能被敌人夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快疏导平民避难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有部队到北端集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一防卫队 溃灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距大岛最终防线还剩2千米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 纳雷因将军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 这里是太平洋圈最大的运输基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦陷落将有数百万人饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要死守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前明明置之不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道学会了人类是如何保命的吗 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人都近在咫尺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 马上就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒纳凯阿没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部下达交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象为大岛全域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部指挥下的空袭部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通新国联总部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的名义下令中止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同伴在作战啊 还有几万平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交战规定α必须严守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺沃尔特少校的权限 逮捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因将军发来中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入坐标 攻击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员搜寻生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…攻击了同伴 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…还有人活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 我们赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…究竟是为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这疲于征战的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将诞生于世界一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:51.06,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\fad(1000,1000)}苍穹之FAFNER EXODUS
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战乱毁灭了日本之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保留和平文化而建造的人工岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我过去的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是地区对抗赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香知道了 要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香三香 你不用太起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 是咲良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们休息会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那孩子 就会想起以前的一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下班去一骑那里吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你不喜欢我做的菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马广登特别篇 追寻神秘巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了几个节目啊 白痴广登
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹也太惯着他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 又闲又热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我想去ALVIS工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老学些战斗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要继承岛上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好 里奈学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你昨天不是买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是用来保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镝木 你是学生会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老买漫画 七夕祭都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个…里奈学姐不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议程就进展不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去一骑学长那里一起开会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 麻烦学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 里奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我可是在干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机 改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:40.97,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,663)}Mk.Sechs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腕部驱动系统 组装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进行FTP实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认连接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进步哦 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈教得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我是乘员兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里待一整天要憋出病来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去一骑那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓 都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不希望任何人再驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然又要组装这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到卡诺恩会去学当工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻本事可不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说想请教保叔你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是引退吧 还得继续画这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是驾驶员培训教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尾老师的要求可没法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去老地方吃咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗 赶不上午餐时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御门 给您搬到里面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老爸教我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这边了 一骑哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午的研究结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像还在准备 我等下再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,员工伙食就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 新产品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不过谁做的就冠谁的名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如一骑咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沟口叔擅自起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很尊敬一骑学长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见和沟口叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上 最近都没下来过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为能和远见学姐一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天箭呼叫管制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.93,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,663)}Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪不明机体 输入导引装置信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标F1（导弹发射）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷斯呼叫天箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.57,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,663)}Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快也不能把屁股送给敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你坐在大飞机上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕不怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽真是的 最近总是那样和空想的朋友说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为没有其他同龄的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我觉得也不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感受性很强 总是令人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐飞机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了呢 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩的蜜瓜冰淇淋苏打 给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赠品 给常客的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见选了航空 卡诺恩选了工科
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司选了医疗 要则是教育
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都决定了前途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士是搞研究吗 挺适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 就在咖啡厅做菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地挺合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不想浪费前王牌驾驶员的宝贵经验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当教官也不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了Fafner也不会消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尼伯龙根连接造成的小规模同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会发现治疗方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学了什么 开始去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望它半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是这样吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有恢复的可能性 不要悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有悲观 还剩3年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么长时间 也能做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我眼睛也看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里那样平静 是重要的同伴曾经待过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 乙姫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直守护着岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了乙姫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对什么有反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC 不明机体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,90秒后将到达护盾防线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标接触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标遭遇 对照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp2}C-300 超星系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.80,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(707,663)\fs28\fscx90}Super Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军大型运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很漂亮的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉似乎也感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让我们见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷斯呼叫CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天箭 追踪接触
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习中的红隼发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,663)}Kestrel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军运输机正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护盾圈外确认到不明质量虫洞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门无应答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全格纳库进入迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1 第2磁冠护盾已展开完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持航路 Fafner待机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出手 敌人还未发现岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有人类军被追击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住区请求通信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.90,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}拜托 妈妈 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.64,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}没事的 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.45,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}冷静点 现在正在帮你拜托人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她说「请救救飞机」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.78,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}今日计划出勤的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:31.56,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}请立即转移至紧急起飞状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:35.70,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}各位岛民请避免外出 等待新的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.96,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}伴随紧急起飞状态 第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 戈班真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗 你昨天不是也买了一样的杂志？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:43.12,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}第一种警戒态势(Waffe laden)已准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:46.20,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}向岛防卫队 刚瑠岛后格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.41,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}庆树岛格纳库部队 以及预备候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.54,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}请立即转移至待机室…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改成出击请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个视频照明不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不要做那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会再陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是实战 我们也能乘坐Fafner吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接测试都没做过？多半参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我还没像广登学长一样做好头盔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学长交托给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广登学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗 把护身符给人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能乘坐Fafner也只有几年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趁现在传承下去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能先出手攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人极有可能于200秒以内实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向50 速度减慢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除部分护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红隼引导运输机降落海面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC呼叫格雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按规定开始引导
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入代码
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫天箭 这是毕业测试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫飞行中的C-300
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是FA3 代号天箭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢通信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是C-300 代号鲸鱼
